nodes.text: Quebe-Luxfause Systems was a company that manufactured queblux-powered technology at the time of the Galactic Civil War. They had a headquarters in Tatooine's spaceport of Mos Eisley.
Quebe-Luxfase was first mentioned in Galaxy Guide 7: Mos Eisley and later canonised in the 2016 version of Star Wars: Complete Locations.
